### Prerequisites

- **Docker** installed and running
- **Access credentials** (if using private registry)

### Pulling the Image

```bash
# Login to registry (if needed)
echo $TOKEN | docker login [registry] -u USERNAME --password-stdin

# Pull the image
docker pull [registry]/[image]:latest
```

### Usage

```bash
# Basic usage
docker run --rm -v $(pwd):/workspace [image]:latest [args]

# With environment variables
docker run --rm -e VAR=value -v $(pwd):/workspace [image]:latest [args]
```

